- Next.js 16 App Router only. No Pages Router.
- TypeScript strict. No `any` types.
- Tailwind CSS v4 only. No inline styles. No CSS modules.
- In Tailwind v4, all theme tokens are defined in globals.css via @theme. Do not use tailwind.config.ts for tokens.
- All images via next/image with width, height, alt.
- All navigation via next/link. No <a> tags.
- Mobile-first. Base styles for 375px, then md: lg: breakpoints.
- No shadcn, no MUI, no external component libraries.
- Colors: only sol.* tokens defined in tailwind.config.ts.
- Fonts: Cormorant Garamond (headings), DM Sans (body).
- Sections padding: py-24 md:py-32. Never feel cramped.
- No pure black (#000). Use sol-bark for all text.
- Rounded corners: rounded-none or rounded-sm maximum.
- No icon libraries. SVG inline only where strictly necessary.